<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Install Quest Planner</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=MedievalSharp&family=Crimson+Text:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
      color: #e8e6e3;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .install-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-family: 'MedievalSharp', cursive;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #d4a843;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .header p {
      color: #a8a5a0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.9);
      border: 2px solid #3d3d3d;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-family: 'MedievalSharp', cursive;
      color: #d4a843;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #d4a843;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    input[type="text"],
    input[type="password"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border: 1px solid #3d3d3d;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #e8e6e3;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #d4a843;
    }

    .form-hint {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #888;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: #d4a843;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-family: 'MedievalSharp', cursive;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #e8c468;
    }

    .error {
      background: rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.2);
      border: 1px solid #c0392b;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #e74c3c;
    }

    .info-box {
      background: rgba(212, 168, 67, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid #d4a843;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .info-box h3 {
      color: #d4a843;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .info-box ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .info-box li {
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 67, 0.2);
    }

    .info-box li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .info-box li strong {
      color: #d4a843;
    }

    .step-indicator {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .step {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(212, 168, 67, 0.2);
      border: 2px solid #d4a843;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'MedievalSharp', cursive;
      color: #d4a843;
    }

    .step.active {
      background: #d4a843;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="install-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>‚öîÔ∏è Quest Planner Setup</h1>
      <p>Let's get your D&D session planner ready!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step-indicator">
      <div class="step active">1</div>
      <div class="step">2</div>
      <div class="step">3</div>
    </div>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="error">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Installation Error</strong><br>
        <%- error %>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="info-box">
      <h3>üìã Before You Begin</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Node.js:</strong> Make sure Node.js 14+ is installed</li>
        <li><strong>Dependencies:</strong> Run <code>npm install</code> before installation</li>
        <li><strong>Permissions:</strong> Ensure write access to the <code>data/</code> directory</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <form method="POST" action="/install">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>üîê Administrator Account</h2>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="admin_username">Admin Username</label>
          <input type="text" id="admin_username" name="admin_username" required minlength="3" placeholder="admin" autocomplete="off">
          <small class="form-hint">This will be your main admin account (minimum 3 characters)</small>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="admin_password">Admin Password</label>
          <input type="password" id="admin_password" name="admin_password" required minlength="6" placeholder="‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢" autocomplete="new-password">
          <small class="form-hint">Choose a strong password (minimum 6 characters)</small>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="admin_password_confirm">Confirm Password</label>
          <input type="password" id="admin_password_confirm" name="admin_password_confirm" required minlength="6" placeholder="‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢‚Ä¢" autocomplete="new-password">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>‚öôÔ∏è Application Settings</h2>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="app_name">Application Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="app_name" name="app_name" value="Quest Planner" required>
          <small class="form-hint">The name displayed throughout the application</small>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="session_secret">Session Secret (Optional)</label>
          <input type="text" id="session_secret" name="session_secret" placeholder="Auto-generated if left empty">
          <small class="form-hint">Leave empty to auto-generate a secure random secret</small>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>‚ÑπÔ∏è What Happens Next?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>‚úì Database will be created with all necessary tables</li>
          <li>‚úì Admin user will be created with the credentials above</li>
          <li>‚úì Configuration file (.env) will be generated</li>
          <li>‚úì Installation lock file will be created</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="btn">‚öîÔ∏è Install Quest Planner</button>
    </form>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">
      Quest Planner v1.0 &middot; Open Source &middot; GPL-3.0 License
    </p>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Simple client-side validation
    document.querySelector('form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      var password = document.getElementById('admin_password').value;
      var confirm = document.getElementById('admin_password_confirm').value;

      if (password !== confirm) {
        e.preventDefault();
        alert('Passwords do not match!');
        return false;
      }

      if (password.length < 6) {
        e.preventDefault();
        alert('Password must be at least 6 characters long!');
        return false;
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
